WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.580 --> 00:01:35.100 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:38.140 line:80%
=Episode 15=

00:01:43.580 --> 00:01:45.050 line:80%
Mr. Song, you're here

00:01:45.050 --> 00:01:46.770 line:80%
for the Jade Sunflower, right?

00:01:47.580 --> 00:01:49.250 line:80%
Once I take the Bliss Palace

00:01:49.250 --> 00:01:50.820 line:80%
and find the Jade Sunflower,

00:01:50.820 --> 00:01:52.130 line:80%
I'll have someone send it to you.

00:01:52.580 --> 00:01:53.940 line:80%
As for other matters,

00:01:54.380 --> 00:01:55.530 line:80%
you need not trouble yourself.

00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:57.330 line:80%
Zhao's Gu poison isn't cured yet,

00:01:58.020 --> 00:01:59.180 line:80%
so I should stay here.

00:01:59.530 --> 00:02:01.100 line:80%
I also want to help Mr. Mu

00:02:01.690 --> 00:02:03.250 line:80%
eliminate Nie Zhe soon.

00:02:04.940 --> 00:02:07.970 line:80%
To find the Jade Sunflower sooner

00:02:07.970 --> 00:02:08.890 line:80%
and regain your powers,

00:02:09.260 --> 00:02:11.980 line:80%
you'd even collude with
a demon sect member like me?

00:02:12.370 --> 00:02:13.460 line:80%
Collude?

00:02:14.090 --> 00:02:15.490 line:80%
Mr. Mu, what are you talking about?

00:02:15.490 --> 00:02:17.260 line:80%
Yuzhi only meant well.

00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:19.020 line:80%
I was speaking with Mr. Song,

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:20.490 line:80%
why did Zhao follow us in?

00:02:20.490 --> 00:02:21.890 line:80%
I brought Yuzhi here.

00:02:21.890 --> 00:02:23.210 line:80%
Naturally, I must ensure his safety.

00:02:24.460 --> 00:02:25.930 line:80%
Mr. Mu, there's no need to worry.

00:02:26.300 --> 00:02:27.740 line:80%
On this trip to the Li Sect,

00:02:27.740 --> 00:02:29.300 line:80%
I should have protected Zhao.

00:02:29.700 --> 00:02:31.260 line:80%
Yet I let her suffer this calamity.

00:02:31.700 --> 00:02:33.980 line:80%
I'll stop at nothing to find an antidote

00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:35.860 line:80%
and kill the ringleader Nie Zhe.

00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:37.090 line:80%
That is the first reason.

00:02:37.090 --> 00:02:38.580 line:80%
Nie Zhe slaughtered the innocent,

00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:39.740 line:80%
refined corpse slaves and

00:02:39.740 --> 00:02:40.580 line:80%
went against all reason.

00:02:40.590 --> 00:02:41.610 line:80%
The world resents him.

00:02:41.610 --> 00:02:43.930 line:80%
How can the Six Sects of Beichen
stand by?

00:02:43.930 --> 00:02:45.330 line:80%
That is the second reason.

00:02:45.330 --> 00:02:46.490 line:80%
Once I return to the Qingque Sect,

00:02:46.490 --> 00:02:48.740 line:80%
I will report the situation here
to my elders.

00:02:48.740 --> 00:02:49.860 line:80%
I'm sure Master

00:02:49.860 --> 00:02:52.020 line:80%
and the other elders
will approve of my actions.

00:02:53.980 --> 00:02:54.820 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:02:55.300 --> 00:02:56.140 line:80%
You...

00:02:56.860 --> 00:02:57.700 line:80%
You're right.

00:02:58.260 --> 00:02:59.210 line:80%
But,

00:02:59.210 --> 00:03:00.700 line:80%
when it comes to
reporting to our elders,

00:03:00.700 --> 00:03:01.540 line:80%
we'd better

00:03:01.540 --> 00:03:02.860 line:80%
think it over once more.

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:04.210 line:80%
To put it plainly,

00:03:05.050 --> 00:03:07.020 line:80%
it's all for the Jade Sunflower.

00:03:10.300 --> 00:03:11.140 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:03:11.540 --> 00:03:13.460 line:80%
did you brew some medicine for me?

00:03:14.090 --> 00:03:15.420 line:80%
It should be nearly ready, right?

00:03:23.210 --> 00:03:24.090 line:80%
Oh, right,

00:03:24.090 --> 00:03:25.210 line:80%
the herbal garden should be

00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:27.580 line:80%
in the valley five miles to
the left of the Youming Path.

00:03:28.770 --> 00:03:29.810 line:80%
You've worked hard.

00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:30.650 line:80%
Okay.

00:03:46.890 --> 00:03:48.180 line:80%
Why did you pull me out here?

00:03:49.260 --> 00:03:50.890 line:80%
Scared I'd drive Song Yuzhi crazy?

00:03:51.330 --> 00:03:53.460 line:80%
Scared he'd drive you crazy.

00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:56.330 line:80%
Yuzhi is focused and righteous.

00:03:56.330 --> 00:03:58.210 line:80%
No question you ask can stump him.

00:03:58.210 --> 00:03:59.740 line:80%
You'll just end up fuming for nothing.

00:03:59.740 --> 00:04:00.580 line:80%
Why bother?

00:04:03.740 --> 00:04:05.610 line:80%
How focused

00:04:06.180 --> 00:04:07.700 line:80%
and righteous.

00:04:08.490 --> 00:04:10.020 line:80%
Once Miss Cai

00:04:10.020 --> 00:04:11.860 line:80%
shakes off the corpse slave's Gu poison,

00:04:11.860 --> 00:04:13.700 line:80%
leave here soon with

00:04:13.700 --> 00:04:15.180 line:80%
your like-minded senior brother.

00:04:16.090 --> 00:04:17.900 line:80%
After I seize the Bliss Palace treasury,

00:04:18.740 --> 00:04:19.580 line:80%
I'll deliver

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.490 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower to you first.

00:04:21.930 --> 00:04:23.100 line:80%
This place is filthy.

00:04:24.050 --> 00:04:25.340 line:80%
I won't keep you here.

00:04:39.370 --> 00:04:40.250 line:80%
No need for your cure.

00:04:40.930 --> 00:04:41.770 line:80%
I'll leave on my own.

00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:51.140 line:80%
You're not leaving.

00:04:53.610 --> 00:04:54.490 line:80%
Let me go!

00:04:54.490 --> 00:04:55.610 line:80%
I'll say this one last time.

00:04:56.010 --> 00:04:57.130 line:80%
You're not leaving.

00:05:01.810 --> 00:05:02.650 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:03.610 line:80%
I won't.

00:05:03.610 --> 00:05:04.450 line:80%
Mr....

00:05:13.300 --> 00:05:14.140 line:80%
What is it?

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:16.910 line:80%
Xing has prepared a herbal bath
for Miss Feng.

00:05:17.150 --> 00:05:18.340 line:80%
Miss Feng, please come over.

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:23.940 line:80%
Please.

00:05:31.930 --> 00:05:33.810 line:80%
If it weren't for you
saving me this time,

00:05:35.010 --> 00:05:36.740 line:80%
I'd have died at Mu Qingyan

00:05:37.690 --> 00:05:39.050 line:80%
and that sorceress's hands.

00:05:39.050 --> 00:05:41.900 line:80%
Never thought she'd be
Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:05:41.900 --> 00:05:44.370 line:80%
I hate that I didn't kill her then.

00:05:44.370 --> 00:05:47.180 line:80%
To avenge Master and the brothers

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:49.050 line:80%
who died by Cai Pingshu's sword.

00:05:51.900 --> 00:05:53.340 line:80%
Next time we meet,

00:05:54.540 --> 00:05:55.780 line:80%
I won't spare her.

00:05:56.610 --> 00:05:57.610 line:80%
No need to rush.

00:05:58.930 --> 00:06:00.130 line:80%
Her identity

00:06:02.100 --> 00:06:04.420 line:80%
might still be useful to us.

00:06:07.450 --> 00:06:09.130 line:80%
Young Master specifically instructed us.

00:06:09.130 --> 00:06:10.450 line:80%
He said Miss Feng

00:06:10.450 --> 00:06:12.690 line:80%
is very particular about
food, clothing, and lodging.

00:06:12.690 --> 00:06:14.340 line:80%
Every decoration in the room

00:06:14.340 --> 00:06:16.370 line:80%
was arranged by Young Master himself.

00:06:16.370 --> 00:06:18.810 line:80%
Young Master is so kind to you,
Miss Feng.

00:06:18.810 --> 00:06:19.740 line:80%
It's okay.

00:06:20.340 --> 00:06:22.220 line:80%
When he was recovering at Qingzhu Gang,

00:06:22.220 --> 00:06:23.490 line:80%
I treated him well too.

00:06:24.180 --> 00:06:25.450 line:80%
Exactly.

00:06:25.450 --> 00:06:27.370 line:80%
Young Master's feelings for you

00:06:27.370 --> 00:06:28.250 line:80%
are undeniable.

00:06:28.570 --> 00:06:29.690 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:06:29.690 --> 00:06:30.530 line:80%
Put it down.

00:06:38.420 --> 00:06:39.300 line:80%
These

00:06:39.300 --> 00:06:41.420 line:80%
are fresh flowers
the Young Master prepared for Miss Feng.

00:06:41.900 --> 00:06:44.050 line:80%
The Young Master is truly thoughtful.

00:06:44.050 --> 00:06:45.010 line:80%
Also,

00:06:45.010 --> 00:06:46.490 line:80%
Mr. Dai has sent word.

00:06:46.490 --> 00:06:48.130 line:80%
He said the herb garden
is still being searched.

00:06:48.130 --> 00:06:49.610 line:80%
Please be patient, Miss Feng.

00:06:49.610 --> 00:06:51.810 line:80%
Qingyun has been searching all night.

00:06:51.810 --> 00:06:53.100 line:80%
Tell him to come back soon.

00:06:53.100 --> 00:06:56.220 line:80%
Mr. Dai values you too, Miss Feng.

00:06:57.810 --> 00:06:59.690 line:80%
That little bit of regard

00:06:59.690 --> 00:07:01.130 line:80%
is nothing

00:07:01.130 --> 00:07:02.810 line:80%
compared to Young Master
and Miss Feng's feelings.

00:07:02.810 --> 00:07:04.340 line:80%
How can you tell?

00:07:04.340 --> 00:07:06.490 line:80%
It's obvious to anyone with eyes.

00:07:06.490 --> 00:07:08.610 line:80%
Though Miss Feng
is skilled in martial arts,

00:07:08.610 --> 00:07:11.450 line:80%
she's still an inexperienced young lady.

00:07:11.450 --> 00:07:13.540 line:80%
Young and lacking experience.

00:07:13.540 --> 00:07:15.570 line:80%
Just worried about
Young Master's safety.

00:07:15.570 --> 00:07:17.610 line:80%
Yet she traveled thousands of li

00:07:17.610 --> 00:07:19.340 line:80%
to this dangerous Hanhai Mountains.

00:07:19.340 --> 00:07:21.900 line:80%
Even as an outsider,

00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:22.980 line:80%
my heart warms hearing that.

00:07:22.980 --> 00:07:24.900 line:80%
If this isn't deep affection,

00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:26.610 line:80%
what is?

00:07:27.540 --> 00:07:28.900 line:80%
I agree.

00:07:28.900 --> 00:07:30.930 line:80%
Miss Feng's loyalty
to Young Master

00:07:30.930 --> 00:07:32.450 line:80%
is truly rare.

00:07:32.450 --> 00:07:34.250 line:80%
This isn't just ordinary affection.

00:07:34.250 --> 00:07:35.810 line:80%
- It's clearly...
- Oh, right.

00:07:35.810 --> 00:07:37.130 line:80%
What was your name again?

00:07:37.130 --> 00:07:38.370 line:80%
My surname is You.

00:07:38.370 --> 00:07:39.810 line:80%
Given name, Guanyue.

00:07:40.250 --> 00:07:41.690 line:80%
Guanyue.

00:07:42.220 --> 00:07:43.060 line:80%
Then, Master You,

00:07:43.370 --> 00:07:44.780 line:80%
do you often read storybooks?

00:07:45.370 --> 00:07:46.220 line:80%
Not really.

00:07:46.420 --> 00:07:47.930 line:80%
In storybooks, there's that kind of man.

00:07:47.930 --> 00:07:49.100 line:80%
For the woman he likes

00:07:49.100 --> 00:07:50.300 line:80%
but can't confess to,

00:07:50.780 --> 00:07:52.490 line:80%
he secretly

00:07:52.490 --> 00:07:54.130 line:80%
plays with her name.

00:07:54.130 --> 00:07:55.000 line:80%
For instance,

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:58.130 line:80%
if that man's name has words
like "Shan" or "Feng,"

00:07:58.130 --> 00:07:59.370 line:80%
he'll fondly call the lady,

00:07:59.370 --> 00:08:00.930 line:80%
"Hua" or "Shui."

00:08:01.340 --> 00:08:02.180 line:80%
Or

00:08:02.740 --> 00:08:04.980 line:80%
"Xing" and "Yue."

00:08:07.300 --> 00:08:08.140 line:80%
Interesting.

00:08:08.490 --> 00:08:09.570 line:80%
Truly interesting.

00:08:10.010 --> 00:08:11.450 line:80%
Why are we suddenly

00:08:11.930 --> 00:08:13.570 line:80%
talking about storybooks?

00:08:14.300 --> 00:08:15.140 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:08:15.340 --> 00:08:17.370 line:80%
Miss Feng and I were just chatting idly.

00:08:22.010 --> 00:08:22.850 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:24.810 line:80%
What is it?

00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:26.250 line:80%
Rumors are spreading everywhere now.

00:08:26.250 --> 00:08:28.860 line:80%
They say you're colluding with
our sect's sworn enemy.

00:08:28.860 --> 00:08:30.050 line:80%
The descendants of Cai Pingshu.

00:08:30.050 --> 00:08:31.250 line:80%
And plan to overturn the Li Sect.

00:08:35.850 --> 00:08:36.810 line:80%
What?

00:08:36.810 --> 00:08:38.300 line:80%
Dad went to the Hanhai Mountains?

00:08:38.300 --> 00:08:39.500 line:80%
When Master left the mountain,

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:41.330 line:80%
he only told me to
handle sect affairs properly.

00:08:41.330 --> 00:08:42.810 line:80%
Didn't say where he was going.

00:08:42.810 --> 00:08:44.450 line:80%
But today a spy reported to Uncle Li.

00:08:44.450 --> 00:08:45.420 line:80%
He said Master and Lord Song

00:08:45.420 --> 00:08:47.140 line:80%
were spotted near the Hanhai Mountains.

00:08:47.140 --> 00:08:48.780 line:80%
I suspect

00:08:48.780 --> 00:08:50.450 line:80%
the demon sect is having major upheaval.

00:08:50.450 --> 00:08:51.810 line:80%
So Master went in person,

00:08:51.810 --> 00:08:53.050 line:80%
without disciples or men.

00:08:55.900 --> 00:08:56.740 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:09:00.090 --> 00:09:00.970 line:80%
To find Father.

00:09:00.970 --> 00:09:01.970 line:80%
To seek Yuzhi.

00:09:01.970 --> 00:09:03.260 line:80%
Yuzhi went to the demon sect too?

00:09:03.260 --> 00:09:04.260 line:80%
When?

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:05.380 line:80%
Cai Zhao went as well.

00:09:05.380 --> 00:09:06.620 line:80%
They left the mountain together.

00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.260 line:80%
Stop!

00:09:10.690 --> 00:09:11.620 line:80%
Mother.

00:09:11.620 --> 00:09:13.090 line:80%
Stay quietly within the sect.

00:09:15.450 --> 00:09:16.930 line:80%
What can you do if you rush over now?

00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:18.100 line:80%
I…

00:09:18.450 --> 00:09:19.500 line:80%
I can help Father.

00:09:19.500 --> 00:09:20.850 line:80%
Why did your father go alone?

00:09:20.850 --> 00:09:22.090 line:80%
He wished to keep this matter quiet.

00:09:22.090 --> 00:09:23.180 line:80%
You rushed over in such a hurry.

00:09:23.180 --> 00:09:25.380 line:80%
Do you want
the whole sect to know about it?

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:26.540 line:80%
If Yuzhi is safe, great.

00:09:26.540 --> 00:09:27.380 line:80%
If not,

00:09:27.380 --> 00:09:28.500 line:80%
how will you fix it?

00:09:29.180 --> 00:09:30.020 line:80%
I...

00:09:31.540 --> 00:09:33.210 line:80%
I know you can't let go.

00:09:33.210 --> 00:09:34.970 line:80%
But if you still want to marry Yuzhi,

00:09:34.970 --> 00:09:36.730 line:80%
you must learn to
prioritize the bigger picture.

00:09:36.730 --> 00:09:37.850 line:80%
Don't be

00:09:37.850 --> 00:09:39.090 line:80%
too rigid about some things.

00:09:39.570 --> 00:09:40.420 line:80%
Pretend

00:09:40.970 --> 00:09:42.330 line:80%
you don't know some things.

00:09:42.850 --> 00:09:43.690 line:80%
Mother,

00:09:43.690 --> 00:09:45.500 line:80%
I'm not as skilled as Cai Zhao,

00:09:45.500 --> 00:09:47.420 line:80%
but I'm not useless either.

00:09:47.420 --> 00:09:49.380 line:80%
With your Father and Uncle there,

00:09:49.380 --> 00:09:51.500 line:80%
they'll surely keep Yuzhi safe.

00:09:51.500 --> 00:09:52.380 line:80%
Besides,

00:09:52.380 --> 00:09:54.570 line:80%
that Cai girl is very proud.

00:09:54.570 --> 00:09:56.180 line:80%
She won't do anything shameful

00:09:56.180 --> 00:09:57.780 line:80%
to dishonor Luoying Valley.

00:10:00.090 --> 00:10:02.420 line:80%
Miss Feng is Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:10:02.420 --> 00:10:03.570 line:80%
Is that for real?

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:04.940 line:80%
Last time at the Xuanwu Altar,

00:10:05.050 --> 00:10:06.930 line:80%
I had doubts
when I saw the Sunshine Blade.

00:10:06.930 --> 00:10:07.770 line:80%
Never thought

00:10:08.380 --> 00:10:09.230 line:80%
she truly was the heir

00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:10.500 line:80%
of that devil Cai Pingshu.

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:12.380 line:80%
Back then,
the former Chief refined corpse slaves,

00:10:13.260 --> 00:10:14.730 line:80%
and captured many Six Sects disciples.

00:10:15.330 --> 00:10:17.380 line:80%
Cai Pingshu stormed
the Youming Path three times

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:19.050 line:80%
and killed countless sect members.

00:10:19.450 --> 00:10:20.450 line:80%
If this news leaks,

00:10:20.780 --> 00:10:22.180 line:80%
the Young Master
will be in a terrible spot.

00:10:23.900 --> 00:10:25.300 line:80%
Then we have to cover it up!

00:10:25.300 --> 00:10:27.620 line:80%
The entire Li Sect
submits to Young Master now.

00:10:27.620 --> 00:10:29.690 line:80%
If Cai Pingshu's heir pops up,

00:10:29.690 --> 00:10:30.930 line:80%
what then?

00:10:30.930 --> 00:10:32.140 line:80%
Attack the Bliss Palace or not?

00:10:32.140 --> 00:10:33.540 line:80%
Go for the Chief position or not?

00:10:33.540 --> 00:10:34.420 line:80%
The only way now is

00:10:34.420 --> 00:10:36.020 line:80%
to persuade Young Master to cut ties

00:10:36.020 --> 00:10:37.050 line:80%
with Miss Cai immediately.

00:10:38.500 --> 00:10:40.180 line:80%
Cai Pingshu is Cai Pingshu.

00:10:40.180 --> 00:10:41.900 line:80%
Miss Cai is Miss Cai.

00:10:41.900 --> 00:10:42.970 line:80%
What's wrong with

00:10:42.970 --> 00:10:44.420 line:80%
the Young Master liking a girl?

00:10:46.330 --> 00:10:47.170 line:80%
Xing,

00:10:47.500 --> 00:10:49.540 line:80%
it's not about liking or not.

00:10:49.540 --> 00:10:51.420 line:80%
Cai Pingshu killed
so many elders of the Li Sect,

00:10:52.870 --> 00:10:54.210 line:80%
including Elder Shangguan's uncle,

00:10:54.210 --> 00:10:55.300 line:80%
Elder Yaoguang,

00:10:55.900 --> 00:10:56.850 line:80%
and even my adoptive father,

00:10:57.330 --> 00:10:58.300 line:80%
Elder Qiu.

00:10:58.900 --> 00:11:00.780 line:80%
All nearly perished
at Cai Pingshu's hands.

00:11:01.140 --> 00:11:02.450 line:80%
How could such a blood feud

00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:04.450 line:80%
be settled?

00:11:05.930 --> 00:11:08.620 line:80%
But Young Master always has a cold face.

00:11:08.620 --> 00:11:10.730 line:80%
Only when he sees Miss Cai

00:11:11.260 --> 00:11:13.450 line:80%
does he crack a small smile.

00:11:15.090 --> 00:11:15.930 line:80%
Can't

00:11:16.540 --> 00:11:18.380 line:80%
we just deny the rumors outright?

00:11:18.380 --> 00:11:20.850 line:80%
Pretend Miss Cai is still Miss Feng.

00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:22.180 line:80%
These rumors

00:11:22.850 --> 00:11:24.730 line:80%
were likely spread on purpose
by someone.

00:11:24.730 --> 00:11:26.140 line:80%
Young Master can't just deny them.

00:11:26.140 --> 00:11:27.690 line:80%
Back then, the Young Master's father

00:11:27.690 --> 00:11:29.050 line:80%
let his emotions rule him,

00:11:29.850 --> 00:11:31.260 line:80%
so he lived a miserable half-life

00:11:31.850 --> 00:11:33.180 line:80%
and died young.

00:11:36.140 --> 00:11:37.060 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:11:37.090 --> 00:11:38.900 line:80%
Why hasn't Yuzhi returned yet?

00:11:40.850 --> 00:11:41.690 line:80%
Miss Feng.

00:11:43.620 --> 00:11:44.460 line:80%
Xing.

00:11:46.850 --> 00:11:48.090 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:11:49.970 --> 00:11:50.810 line:80%
I heard...

00:11:50.870 --> 00:11:52.420 line:80%
the village chief and the others
are leaving.

00:11:52.780 --> 00:11:54.450 line:80%
Yes. Young Master is kind.

00:11:54.660 --> 00:11:56.090 line:80%
Afraid Nie Zhe
will take revenge secretly.

00:11:56.690 --> 00:11:58.260 line:80%
He wants them to come back

00:11:58.260 --> 00:11:59.900 line:80%
when the sect is more stable.

00:11:59.900 --> 00:12:01.810 line:80%
Look, Young Master specially

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:03.210 line:80%
told me to hand out these

00:12:03.210 --> 00:12:04.420 line:80%
insect repellent sachets to everyone.

00:12:07.930 --> 00:12:08.770 line:80%
Xing,

00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:11.050 line:80%
help me pass a message to Uncle Xue,

00:12:11.380 --> 00:12:12.220 line:80%
just tell him

00:12:12.540 --> 00:12:14.180 line:80%
I need his help with something.

00:12:21.260 --> 00:12:22.780 line:80%
Sunshine Blade?

00:12:23.730 --> 00:12:26.020 line:80%
She really is Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:12:26.850 --> 00:12:27.850 line:80%
If I'd known,

00:12:28.380 --> 00:12:30.050 line:80%
I never would've saved you.

00:12:30.330 --> 00:12:31.260 line:80%
Back in the day,

00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:32.930 line:80%
the former Chief and countless members

00:12:33.380 --> 00:12:35.420 line:80%
died horribly at Cai Pingshu's hands.

00:12:35.780 --> 00:12:36.620 line:80%
Cai clan

00:12:37.380 --> 00:12:40.380 line:80%
and our Li Sect are mortal enemies!

00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:41.420 line:80%
She's her.

00:12:41.420 --> 00:12:42.730 line:80%
Her aunt is her aunt.

00:12:43.020 --> 00:12:44.540 line:80%
Elder Yan, don't you forget.

00:12:44.810 --> 00:12:46.020 line:80%
Back at the Xuanwu Altar,

00:12:46.330 --> 00:12:48.330 line:80%
Miss Cai saved Young Master

00:12:48.330 --> 00:12:49.570 line:80%
and so many of our members.

00:12:49.570 --> 00:12:50.570 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:12:50.940 --> 00:12:53.380 line:80%
The Six Sects of Beichen
are always hypocritical and deceitful.

00:12:53.850 --> 00:12:56.020 line:80%
Who knows if she's
bewitching Young Master?

00:12:56.020 --> 00:12:56.860 line:80%
Today,

00:12:56.880 --> 00:12:58.620 line:80%
I'll eliminate this traitor for Li Sect.

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:01.620 line:80%
I won't let our 200-year legacy

00:13:01.620 --> 00:13:03.180 line:80%
be destroyed by a Cai clan woman!

00:13:03.180 --> 00:13:05.380 line:80%
Zhao and I came here with no ill intent.

00:13:05.380 --> 00:13:07.020 line:80%
But if you keep threatening us
with weapons,

00:13:07.020 --> 00:13:08.780 line:80%
we won't surrender willingly.

00:13:08.780 --> 00:13:10.140 line:80%
It's just a battle.

00:13:10.570 --> 00:13:11.410 line:80%
Enough.

00:13:21.090 --> 00:13:21.930 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:13:22.330 --> 00:13:23.420 line:80%
what do you mean by this?

00:13:23.930 --> 00:13:27.090 line:80%
Mr. Mu keeps getting entangled with
this Cai witch.

00:13:27.090 --> 00:13:28.180 line:80%
Are you

00:13:28.180 --> 00:13:30.970 line:80%
abandoning the entire Li Sect?

00:13:30.970 --> 00:13:32.380 line:80%
So the rumors are true.

00:13:32.380 --> 00:13:34.450 line:80%
Young Master really is
in cahoots with the Six Sects' devils.

00:13:34.450 --> 00:13:36.500 line:80%
This woman really is
that devil Cai Pingshu's heir.

00:13:36.970 --> 00:13:37.810 line:80%
Elder Yan.

00:13:38.300 --> 00:13:40.730 line:80%
It's clearly a setup to stir up trouble.

00:13:41.090 --> 00:13:42.970 line:80%
We can't fall for it!

00:13:43.620 --> 00:13:45.690 line:80%
Miss Cai has done our Li Sect
a great favor.

00:13:45.690 --> 00:13:46.540 line:80%
Why not

00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:48.730 line:80%
let bygones be bygones?

00:13:48.730 --> 00:13:50.210 line:80%
Just let her
leave the Hanhai Mountains...

00:13:50.210 --> 00:13:52.420 line:80%
A bunch of bitter, useless fools.

00:13:52.730 --> 00:13:54.140 line:80%
Back in the Battle of Mount Tu,

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:56.780 line:80%
when Cai Pingshu fought Nie Hengcheng,

00:13:56.780 --> 00:13:57.970 line:80%
did she use hidden weapons?

00:13:58.380 --> 00:13:59.730 line:80%
Did she set a trap?

00:14:00.970 --> 00:14:02.380 line:80%
Did she win by outnumbering his foe?

00:14:03.420 --> 00:14:05.380 line:80%
It was a fair fight to the death.

00:14:06.210 --> 00:14:07.570 line:80%
Victory or defeat was fate.

00:14:08.140 --> 00:14:09.730 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was a generation older

00:14:09.730 --> 00:14:11.380 line:80%
and over ten years older

00:14:11.620 --> 00:14:13.380 line:80%
than Cai Pingshu.

00:14:13.900 --> 00:14:15.570 line:80%
Yet in the end, he was outmatched.

00:14:15.930 --> 00:14:17.180 line:80%
He was killed and beheaded.

00:14:17.420 --> 00:14:19.620 line:80%
Such disgrace brought upon us.

00:14:20.330 --> 00:14:21.810 line:80%
And you still dare to speak of it.

00:14:22.690 --> 00:14:23.730 line:80%
Do you feel no shame?

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:27.620 line:80%
The Li Sect has hidden
in the Hanhai Mountains

00:14:27.620 --> 00:14:28.690 line:80%
for 200 years.

00:14:30.090 --> 00:14:31.900 line:80%
It's time to step out into the world.

00:14:32.380 --> 00:14:34.020 line:80%
Now the mountain gate is open.

00:14:34.380 --> 00:14:35.930 line:80%
Stay or leave,

00:14:37.090 --> 00:14:38.380 line:80%
it's your choice.

00:14:40.810 --> 00:14:42.210 line:80%
As for Cai Pingshu's niece,

00:14:42.780 --> 00:14:44.140 line:80%
she's my closest friend.

00:14:45.050 --> 00:14:47.180 line:80%
If anyone here dares harm her,

00:14:48.140 --> 00:14:49.500 line:80%
I'll kill them.

00:14:50.260 --> 00:14:51.380 line:80%
Without the slightest mercy.

00:14:53.930 --> 00:14:55.450 line:80%
For over a hundred years

00:14:55.450 --> 00:14:57.420 line:80%
the Mu clan has always acted

00:14:57.420 --> 00:14:58.970 line:80%
without thinking.

00:14:58.970 --> 00:15:00.500 line:80%
Letting emotions rule.

00:15:00.500 --> 00:15:01.420 line:80%
At best,

00:15:01.420 --> 00:15:03.140 line:80%
it tears families apart.

00:15:03.140 --> 00:15:03.980 line:80%
At worst,

00:15:04.690 --> 00:15:06.570 line:80%
it brings bloodshed to the sect.

00:15:07.090 --> 00:15:07.970 line:80%
Fine.

00:15:07.970 --> 00:15:10.380 line:80%
I'll see how this ends for you.

00:15:10.970 --> 00:15:11.810 line:80%
Go!

00:15:15.810 --> 00:15:16.650 line:80%
Guanyue.

00:15:17.900 --> 00:15:18.930 line:80%
If they wish to leave,

00:15:20.210 --> 00:15:21.050 line:80%
let them go.

00:15:21.540 --> 00:15:22.380 line:80%
Don't stop them.

00:15:23.620 --> 00:15:24.810 line:80%
Also, find out

00:15:25.450 --> 00:15:28.210 line:80%
who's spreading these rumors.

00:15:29.420 --> 00:15:30.850 line:80%
Kill them without mercy.

00:15:31.780 --> 00:15:33.260 line:80%
Yes, Mr. Mu.

00:15:40.930 --> 00:15:42.180 line:80%
Have you found the herb garden?

00:15:48.730 --> 00:15:49.850 line:80%
Everyone behind, keep up.

00:15:49.850 --> 00:15:51.260 line:80%
Hurry, hurry and keep up.

00:15:51.260 --> 00:15:52.540 line:80%
Keep up, let's go.

00:15:52.540 --> 00:15:53.380 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:15:54.210 --> 00:15:55.050 line:80%
Go.

00:15:55.690 --> 00:15:56.530 line:80%
Brother.

00:15:58.420 --> 00:15:59.810 line:80%
May I ask you something?

00:15:59.810 --> 00:16:00.650 line:80%
What's happening

00:16:00.650 --> 00:16:01.930 line:80%
at the Li Sect?

00:16:01.930 --> 00:16:03.620 line:80%
Where's all this fire coming from?

00:16:03.620 --> 00:16:04.810 line:80%
Mr. Mu is kind.

00:16:04.810 --> 00:16:07.300 line:80%
He ordered the nightmare fields burned
and left an exit

00:16:07.300 --> 00:16:08.810 line:80%
for us villagers to leave safely.

00:16:10.260 --> 00:16:12.330 line:80%
Mr. Mu is truly extraordinary.

00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:16.090 line:80%
May I ask, in these past days,

00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:18.330 line:80%
have you seen anyone from the Six Sects?

00:16:18.540 --> 00:16:19.690 line:80%
I did hear

00:16:20.380 --> 00:16:21.270 line:80%
that there's

00:16:21.270 --> 00:16:22.380 line:80%
Cai Pingshu's niece here.

00:16:22.900 --> 00:16:24.300 line:80%
She plans to join hands with Mr. Mu

00:16:24.300 --> 00:16:25.420 line:80%
to strike against Chief Nie.

00:16:27.500 --> 00:16:28.340 line:80%
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

00:16:31.090 --> 00:16:33.690 line:80%
Just find the Jade Sunflower quietly.

00:16:33.690 --> 00:16:35.850 line:80%
Why get tangled up with Mr. Mu?

00:16:35.850 --> 00:16:36.850 line:80%
No point in talking more.

00:16:36.850 --> 00:16:38.140 line:80%
Let's go in and see for ourselves.

00:16:38.420 --> 00:16:39.260 line:80%
Lord Song.

00:16:43.140 --> 00:16:44.570 line:80%
You... know me?

00:16:44.810 --> 00:16:45.650 line:80%
I don't.

00:16:46.050 --> 00:16:47.300 line:80%
Someone told me,

00:16:47.300 --> 00:16:49.970 line:80%
if a man is well-dressed, imposing,

00:16:50.120 --> 00:16:51.090 line:80%
and has a slight belly,

00:16:51.540 --> 00:16:53.180 line:80%
it must be Lord Song.

00:16:53.850 --> 00:16:54.690 line:80%
Did this person

00:16:54.850 --> 00:16:56.810 line:80%
have a message for us?

00:16:57.050 --> 00:16:58.420 line:80%
You must be Lord Qi.

00:16:58.420 --> 00:16:59.620 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:59.620 --> 00:17:01.210 line:80%
Then I'll deliver the message.

00:17:02.380 --> 00:17:03.970 line:80%
"Master, forgive me."

00:17:03.970 --> 00:17:05.770 line:80%
"I've disappointed you again."

00:17:05.770 --> 00:17:07.420 line:80%
"Once I return,
I won't run off anymore."

00:17:08.490 --> 00:17:09.330 line:80%
This girl...

00:17:10.210 --> 00:17:11.060 line:80%
"Lord Song."

00:17:11.060 --> 00:17:12.770 line:80%
"What Yuzhi is looking for
is right here."

00:17:12.770 --> 00:17:14.010 line:80%
"You'd better not go in."

00:17:14.010 --> 00:17:16.420 line:80%
"Or complications
might make us lose it."

00:17:17.820 --> 00:17:18.820 line:80%
Alright.

00:17:19.420 --> 00:17:20.260 line:80%
Message delivered.

00:17:20.530 --> 00:17:21.420 line:80%
You two,

00:17:21.420 --> 00:17:22.270 line:80%
I'll take my leave.

00:17:22.620 --> 00:17:23.490 line:80%
Thank you.

00:17:27.120 --> 00:17:29.860 line:80%
How did these two kids get involved in
the demon sect's civil strife?

00:17:30.250 --> 00:17:32.010 line:80%
There's no hiding it anymore.

00:17:32.290 --> 00:17:33.530 line:80%
We both ordered

00:17:33.530 --> 00:17:34.860 line:80%
Zhao and Yuzhi

00:17:34.860 --> 00:17:36.490 line:80%
to the demon sect for intelligence.

00:17:36.490 --> 00:17:37.330 line:80%
But

00:17:37.780 --> 00:17:39.180 line:80%
they were discovered by the demon sect.

00:17:39.730 --> 00:17:40.970 line:80%
That's how the rumors started.

00:17:42.180 --> 00:17:43.140 line:80%
Yunke,

00:17:43.140 --> 00:17:46.140 line:80%
I always thought
you were slow and rigid.

00:17:46.140 --> 00:17:48.340 line:80%
Never knew you were
so clever and flexible.

00:17:59.930 --> 00:18:02.290 line:80%
Xiong Qianjin treated
that woman with great respect.

00:18:02.290 --> 00:18:04.970 line:80%
So I guessed she holds
a high position in the Li Sect.

00:18:04.970 --> 00:18:06.620 line:80%
Too bad we're one step too late.

00:18:07.100 --> 00:18:08.380 line:80%
What did Xiong Qianjin call her?

00:18:08.820 --> 00:18:09.970 line:80%
He called her Lady Sun.

00:18:15.420 --> 00:18:16.620 line:80%
Look at these roots.

00:18:16.620 --> 00:18:19.180 line:80%
They're the same as the herbs
Lady Sun had.

00:18:22.180 --> 00:18:23.140 line:80%
It's poison smoke.

00:18:23.630 --> 00:18:24.970 line:80%
Destroying the herbs isn't enough.

00:18:24.970 --> 00:18:26.490 line:80%
They also laid such a vicious trap.

00:18:26.770 --> 00:18:28.380 line:80%
Such an elaborate setup.

00:18:28.620 --> 00:18:30.100 line:80%
Seems we're on the right track.

00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:34.140 line:80%
Black roots, short hairs.

00:18:34.140 --> 00:18:35.250 line:80%
I've never seen a plant like this

00:18:35.250 --> 00:18:36.900 line:80%
in the Compendium of Herbs.

00:18:36.900 --> 00:18:38.060 line:80%
It's the Beichen Orchid.

00:18:38.060 --> 00:18:40.060 line:80%
This herb really can
prolong life and detoxify.

00:18:40.060 --> 00:18:41.820 line:80%
Zhao, I'll take you somewhere.

00:18:42.730 --> 00:18:43.570 line:80%
Oh right.

00:18:43.570 --> 00:18:45.100 line:80%
This is the Li Sect's forbidden ground.

00:18:45.730 --> 00:18:47.100 line:80%
No outsiders are allowed in.

00:18:47.100 --> 00:18:48.040 line:80%
Then I...

00:18:48.040 --> 00:18:48.960 line:80%
You're not an outsider.

00:18:49.100 --> 00:18:49.940 line:80%
Let's go.

00:18:54.300 --> 00:18:57.580 line:80%
(Carefree)

00:19:00.930 --> 00:19:02.060 line:80%
This is Carefree.

00:19:03.140 --> 00:19:05.380 line:80%
Every brick and tile,
every blade of grass and tree.

00:19:06.060 --> 00:19:08.210 line:80%
All were personally overseen
by my father.

00:19:08.970 --> 00:19:10.340 line:80%
Your father had fine taste.

00:19:13.380 --> 00:19:14.730 line:80%
After he passed away,

00:19:15.060 --> 00:19:16.860 line:80%
Uncle Cheng
took over the management here.

00:19:17.860 --> 00:19:19.010 line:80%
That is the Beichen Orchid.

00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:21.490 line:80%
This flower

00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:22.860 line:80%
looks like the Withered Branch.

00:19:22.860 --> 00:19:24.180 line:80%
It was my father's cherished treasure.

00:19:25.860 --> 00:19:27.250 line:80%
Said to be rare in the world.

00:19:27.250 --> 00:19:29.140 line:80%
My father tried many ways.

00:19:29.140 --> 00:19:30.530 line:80%
Only obtained this single plant.

00:19:35.530 --> 00:19:36.380 line:80%
Let's give it a try.

00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:40.230 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:19:40.540 --> 00:19:42.090 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:19:42.390 --> 00:19:45.140 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:47.300 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:19:47.310 --> 00:19:48.780 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:19:48.950 --> 00:19:49.860 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:19:49.870 --> 00:19:52.820 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:19:53.630 --> 00:19:55.180 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:19:55.580 --> 00:19:57.220 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:19:57.480 --> 00:19:58.820 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:00.020 line:80%
Uncle Cheng.

00:20:01.150 --> 00:20:02.100 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:20:02.730 --> 00:20:03.570 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:20:03.590 --> 00:20:04.620 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:20:04.630 --> 00:20:06.860 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:20:07.920 --> 00:20:10.180 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:12.980 line:80%
Zhao.

00:20:15.060 --> 00:20:17.780 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:20:17.880 --> 00:20:21.870 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:20:22.530 --> 00:20:25.230 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:20:25.410 --> 00:20:28.920 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:20:28.930 --> 00:20:29.930 line:80%
It really works.

00:20:30.070 --> 00:20:32.640 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:20:34.420 --> 00:20:35.260 line:80%
Uncle Cheng.

00:20:35.620 --> 00:20:37.450 line:80%
Take the remaining herbs to Guanyue.

00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:38.530 line:80%
Use them to cure Xing

00:20:38.530 --> 00:20:40.140 line:80%
and the sect members'
corpse slave poison.

00:20:40.580 --> 00:20:41.620 line:80%
I'll leave at once.

00:20:42.690 --> 00:20:43.530 line:80%
Uncle Cheng.

00:20:45.340 --> 00:20:46.180 line:80%
Thank you.

00:20:50.930 --> 00:20:51.770 line:80%
Zhao.

00:20:51.970 --> 00:20:52.820 line:80%
What are you up to?

00:20:52.820 --> 00:20:54.180 line:80%
Beichen Orchid is so effective.

00:20:54.730 --> 00:20:57.100 line:80%
Why not try it to
cleanse your poison too?

00:20:57.490 --> 00:20:58.450 line:80%
No need.

00:20:58.450 --> 00:20:59.530 line:80%
What's the harm in a try?

00:21:03.770 --> 00:21:04.860 line:80%
You just recovered.

00:21:05.540 --> 00:21:06.970 line:80%
Don't recklessly use your inner power.

00:21:11.530 --> 00:21:13.210 line:80%
If you really care about me,

00:21:13.820 --> 00:21:15.340 line:80%
after I die from the poison,

00:21:16.140 --> 00:21:17.900 line:80%
ask them for a handful of my ashes

00:21:17.900 --> 00:21:18.740 line:80%
to carry with you.

00:21:20.140 --> 00:21:21.420 line:80%
Who wants to carry your ashes?

00:21:23.340 --> 00:21:24.860 line:80%
Will you forget me, Zhao?

00:21:25.530 --> 00:21:27.690 line:80%
When you have children
and grandchildren,

00:21:28.100 --> 00:21:29.450 line:80%
grow old and gray,

00:21:29.900 --> 00:21:31.900 line:80%
will you never mention me to them?

00:21:32.290 --> 00:21:33.130 line:80%
Me?

00:21:35.820 --> 00:21:37.100 line:80%
Children and grandchildren?

00:21:55.930 --> 00:21:57.140 line:80%
The moon

00:21:58.180 --> 00:21:59.020 line:80%
is so bright tonight.

00:22:10.210 --> 00:22:11.450 line:80%
I often miss

00:22:12.380 --> 00:22:13.490 line:80%
the days we lived together

00:22:14.060 --> 00:22:15.290 line:80%
at Qingque Sect.

00:22:20.900 --> 00:22:21.740 line:80%
Zhao.

00:22:22.380 --> 00:22:23.770 line:80%
Those were my happiest,

00:22:25.620 --> 00:22:27.100 line:80%
and most peaceful days.

00:22:49.010 --> 00:22:50.690 line:80%
This wrist guard is so unique.

00:22:53.100 --> 00:22:54.210 line:80%
Is it yours?

00:22:54.730 --> 00:22:56.060 line:80%
It's a memento from my father.

00:22:59.420 --> 00:23:00.490 line:80%
Since I was little,

00:23:00.490 --> 00:23:01.620 line:80%
I'd often see Father

00:23:01.620 --> 00:23:03.180 line:80%
staring at those wrist guards,
lost in thought.

00:23:04.580 --> 00:23:05.420 line:80%
I think

00:23:05.900 --> 00:23:07.450 line:80%
they must have an extraordinary origin.

00:23:08.290 --> 00:23:10.060 line:80%
That's why Father
treasures them so much.

00:23:17.580 --> 00:23:18.420 line:80%
Zhao,

00:23:20.010 --> 00:23:20.970 line:80%
lie with me for a while.

00:23:21.930 --> 00:23:22.860 line:80%
I'm tired.

00:23:27.490 --> 00:23:28.490 line:80%
What are you up to now?

00:23:39.420 --> 00:23:40.770 line:80%
During my time at the Li Sect,

00:23:43.530 --> 00:23:45.210 line:80%
I've been surrounded by enemies,

00:23:46.060 --> 00:23:47.380 line:80%
worn out from constant worry.

00:23:49.690 --> 00:23:51.180 line:80%
Only when you're by my side

00:23:52.860 --> 00:23:54.380 line:80%
do I feel a little peace.

00:24:07.290 --> 00:24:10.500 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)
Thank you. Thank you.

00:24:10.500 --> 00:24:13.620 line:80%
Thank you. Thank you.

00:24:17.290 --> 00:24:19.060 line:80%
Zhao didn't return all night yesterday.

00:24:19.060 --> 00:24:20.250 line:80%
Has your gu poison been cured?

00:24:20.860 --> 00:24:22.900 line:80%
How do you know she was gone all night?

00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:25.450 line:80%
Were you waiting outside all night?

00:24:25.820 --> 00:24:27.290 line:80%
I came here with Zhao.

00:24:27.290 --> 00:24:29.060 line:80%
I should keep an eye on her safety.

00:24:29.060 --> 00:24:30.420 line:80%
Do you have a problem with that, Mr. Mu?

00:24:32.340 --> 00:24:33.180 line:80%
Zhao.

00:24:34.530 --> 00:24:37.060 line:80%
There are still a few villagers
who need qi healing.

00:24:37.060 --> 00:24:38.290 line:80%
Can you help them?

00:24:38.620 --> 00:24:39.580 line:80%
I'll go right away.

00:24:42.140 --> 00:24:42.980 line:80%
I'll help you.

00:24:43.490 --> 00:24:44.420 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:24:46.380 --> 00:24:47.620 line:80%
May I speak with you privately?

00:24:49.730 --> 00:24:51.450 line:80%
You were the one who

00:24:51.450 --> 00:24:52.340 line:80%
snuck into Carefree, right?

00:24:54.290 --> 00:24:55.490 line:80%
When I was nine,

00:24:56.530 --> 00:24:58.380 line:80%
my mother knew her days were numbered.

00:24:59.060 --> 00:25:00.730 line:80%
She told me many things.

00:25:00.730 --> 00:25:01.770 line:80%
I've heard your mother,

00:25:01.770 --> 00:25:03.010 line:80%
Lady Qinglian,

00:25:03.010 --> 00:25:04.180 line:80%
was extremely wise and resourceful.

00:25:04.180 --> 00:25:05.580 line:80%
May I ask

00:25:05.580 --> 00:25:06.970 line:80%
what advice did she give you

00:25:06.970 --> 00:25:08.010 line:80%
before she passed?

00:25:08.420 --> 00:25:09.490 line:80%
Everything in the world

00:25:10.250 --> 00:25:11.690 line:80%
bows to one word,

00:25:12.860 --> 00:25:13.700 line:80%
"Momentum."

00:25:15.060 --> 00:25:16.340 line:80%
Go with the momentum,

00:25:16.340 --> 00:25:17.530 line:80%
achieve double the result.

00:25:18.340 --> 00:25:19.380 line:80%
Go against it,

00:25:20.060 --> 00:25:22.730 line:80%
and even someone
as mighty as Nie Hengcheng

00:25:23.180 --> 00:25:25.420 line:80%
will end up in ruin.

00:25:25.860 --> 00:25:26.970 line:80%
Then tell me, Song,

00:25:28.210 --> 00:25:29.210 line:80%
what is momentum?

00:25:30.530 --> 00:25:31.620 line:80%
On a cosmic scale,

00:25:32.140 --> 00:25:34.900 line:80%
the sun rises and sets. Rivers flow east.
Mountains stand in silence.

00:25:35.770 --> 00:25:37.250 line:80%
No matter your toil,

00:25:37.250 --> 00:25:38.900 line:80%
the sun still falls as it should.

00:25:39.220 --> 00:25:40.580 line:80%
Even with the blood of a crying cuckoo,

00:25:40.580 --> 00:25:42.180 line:80%
the moon will still return on time.

00:25:42.180 --> 00:25:43.340 line:80%
On a human scale,

00:25:43.930 --> 00:25:45.450 line:80%
it is the fate of a nation or a sect.

00:25:45.450 --> 00:25:46.530 line:80%
A person's path in life.

00:25:47.380 --> 00:25:48.220 line:80%
Or

00:25:49.180 --> 00:25:51.140 line:80%
the success or failure of a marriage.

00:25:51.140 --> 00:25:53.340 line:80%
Just old clichés, really.

00:25:53.340 --> 00:25:54.970 line:80%
I thought the same when I was young.

00:25:55.340 --> 00:25:57.140 line:80%
But everything my mother predicted

00:25:57.580 --> 00:25:59.250 line:80%
came true, without exception.

00:26:00.100 --> 00:26:01.530 line:80%
Mr. Mu, you're extremely intelligent.

00:26:02.580 --> 00:26:03.450 line:80%
Can't you see

00:26:03.450 --> 00:26:05.620 line:80%
the momentum between you and Zhao now?

00:26:06.860 --> 00:26:08.860 line:80%
You were born into the demonic sect,

00:26:08.860 --> 00:26:10.730 line:80%
while she belongs to
the Six Sects of Beichen.

00:26:10.730 --> 00:26:12.210 line:80%
She has loving parents,

00:26:12.210 --> 00:26:13.580 line:80%
caring elders,

00:26:13.580 --> 00:26:14.730 line:80%
and harmonious siblings.

00:26:16.060 --> 00:26:17.690 line:80%
She has so much to cherish.

00:26:18.450 --> 00:26:19.970 line:80%
So that's your point.

00:26:21.290 --> 00:26:24.250 line:80%
I wondered why you had the time to

00:26:24.250 --> 00:26:25.770 line:80%
chat with me about old memories.

00:26:25.770 --> 00:26:26.900 line:80%
Rest assured, Mr. Mu.

00:26:28.060 --> 00:26:30.060 line:80%
I won't say a word or do anything

00:26:30.060 --> 00:26:30.970 line:80%
to interfere with Zhao.

00:26:31.420 --> 00:26:32.260 line:80%
Back then,

00:26:33.010 --> 00:26:33.860 line:80%
she refused to tell me

00:26:33.860 --> 00:26:36.010 line:80%
the details of getting the saliva
from the Polar Snow Mountains.

00:26:36.010 --> 00:26:36.850 line:80%
But I believe

00:26:37.340 --> 00:26:39.340 line:80%
you helped a great deal, Mr. Mu.

00:26:39.970 --> 00:26:42.210 line:80%
Zhao's feelings for you
are beyond doubt.

00:26:42.210 --> 00:26:43.620 line:80%
Nothing others say will change that.

00:26:45.690 --> 00:26:47.450 line:80%
But my mother also said that

00:26:47.860 --> 00:26:49.930 line:80%
no matter how deep the affection,

00:26:50.530 --> 00:26:52.450 line:80%
it can't stand against
the momentum of the world.

00:26:53.860 --> 00:26:55.930 line:80%
Mr. Mu, why force it?

00:26:55.930 --> 00:26:56.770 line:80%
What a coincidence.

00:26:58.490 --> 00:27:00.180 line:80%
I just love forcing things.

00:27:03.290 --> 00:27:04.210 line:80%
It's all done.

00:27:09.820 --> 00:27:11.380 line:80%
What are you two talking about?

00:27:11.860 --> 00:27:12.860 line:80%
So serious.

00:27:14.580 --> 00:27:15.450 line:80%
Just idle chatter.

00:27:27.900 --> 00:27:28.740 line:80%
I heard

00:27:28.900 --> 00:27:31.620 line:80%
Mu Qingyan escaped
the poison smoke in the herb garden.

00:27:31.970 --> 00:27:34.210 line:80%
And cured the corpse slave's gu poison.

00:27:39.930 --> 00:27:40.830 line:80%
Dear,

00:27:40.830 --> 00:27:42.010 line:80%
he's tricky,

00:27:42.110 --> 00:27:43.250 line:80%
but if you need me,

00:27:43.250 --> 00:27:44.210 line:80%
I'll obey your orders.

00:27:44.210 --> 00:27:45.250 line:80%
Dad.

00:27:47.210 --> 00:27:48.050 line:80%
Si'en,

00:27:50.040 --> 00:27:51.430 line:80%
why haven't you done your lessons?

00:27:51.610 --> 00:27:52.610 line:80%
Dad,

00:27:52.750 --> 00:27:56.160 line:80%
I heard the Mu clan is coming to
cause trouble again.

00:27:56.400 --> 00:27:57.940 line:80%
I'm worried about you.

00:27:59.560 --> 00:28:00.770 line:80%
Ruxin,

00:28:00.980 --> 00:28:02.100 line:80%
the child is still young.

00:28:02.100 --> 00:28:04.540 line:80%
No need to tell him such things.

00:28:04.540 --> 00:28:06.380 line:80%
Even if he hears it by chance,

00:28:06.380 --> 00:28:08.340 line:80%
we should guide him properly.

00:28:08.360 --> 00:28:10.990 line:80%
The strategist came to
teach Si'en martial arts today.

00:28:11.100 --> 00:28:13.260 line:80%
Si'en asked why he was injured

00:28:13.260 --> 00:28:15.220 line:80%
and found out naturally.

00:28:15.220 --> 00:28:16.260 line:80%
Besides,

00:28:16.260 --> 00:28:18.260 line:80%
it's common knowledge.

00:28:18.260 --> 00:28:19.860 line:80%
Why hide it?

00:28:20.380 --> 00:28:22.100 line:80%
Do you have any scruples, Sister?

00:28:22.580 --> 00:28:23.660 line:80%
Ruxin,

00:28:24.220 --> 00:28:25.820 line:80%
that's not what I meant.

00:28:29.020 --> 00:28:29.940 line:80%
Dear.

00:28:30.590 --> 00:28:31.660 line:80%
Dad.

00:28:32.220 --> 00:28:35.300 line:80%
Is that Mu Qingyan truly that powerful?

00:28:36.220 --> 00:28:37.260 line:80%
Him?

00:28:37.260 --> 00:28:38.980 line:80%
He's just someone
who should've died long ago.

00:28:39.300 --> 00:28:40.980 line:80%
A loser I defeated before.

00:28:41.380 --> 00:28:42.300 line:80%
Si'en, come here.

00:28:42.940 --> 00:28:45.300 line:80%
Take a look at this
Map of Mountains and Seas.

00:28:45.540 --> 00:28:46.580 line:80%
(Demon Realm)
One day,

00:28:46.580 --> 00:28:47.740 line:80%
all this will be yours.

00:28:48.060 --> 00:28:49.700 line:80%
The Li Sect will belong to
Nie clan from now on.

00:28:50.500 --> 00:28:52.380 line:80%
No longer tied to the Mu clan.

00:28:54.300 --> 00:28:55.380 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:56.020 --> 00:28:57.180 line:80%
Everything will be Si'en's.

00:28:57.300 --> 00:28:58.420 line:80%
Don't touch me.

00:28:59.300 --> 00:29:00.340 line:80%
Alright, Si'en.

00:29:00.340 --> 00:29:01.900 line:80%
Time for you to
get back to your studies.

00:29:03.380 --> 00:29:04.420 line:80%
You all head back first.

00:29:05.260 --> 00:29:06.420 line:80%
I'll come see you tonight.

00:29:06.420 --> 00:29:07.260 line:80%
No need.

00:29:07.650 --> 00:29:09.300 line:80%
Si'en has been sleeping early
these days.

00:29:20.920 --> 00:29:22.460 line:80%
Dear, you treat Ruxin
with such kindness.

00:29:22.980 --> 00:29:24.940 line:80%
Too bad she's so stubborn.

00:29:24.940 --> 00:29:25.810 line:80%
Dear.

00:29:25.810 --> 00:29:27.460 line:80%
Don't be sad.

00:29:27.460 --> 00:29:28.420 line:80%
Let her be.

00:29:28.820 --> 00:29:30.500 line:80%
After all,
she's Uncle's adopted daughter.

00:29:31.100 --> 00:29:33.780 line:80%
And the wife
Uncle personally chose for me.

00:29:34.560 --> 00:29:35.420 line:80%
In truth,

00:29:35.420 --> 00:29:36.580 line:80%
I've long wanted to

00:29:36.580 --> 00:29:38.020 line:80%
make you my co-wife.

00:29:38.740 --> 00:29:39.700 line:80%
But unfortunately,

00:29:40.260 --> 00:29:42.660 line:80%
you can't let go of your son.

00:29:47.900 --> 00:29:49.980 line:80%
Chief, I can never repay your kindness.

00:29:50.620 --> 00:29:52.060 line:80%
I know my status is low.

00:29:52.060 --> 00:29:53.340 line:80%
I don't dare hope for such things.

00:29:54.110 --> 00:29:55.100 line:80%
But for the Chief,

00:29:55.100 --> 00:29:56.030 line:80%
for the Li Sect,

00:29:56.040 --> 00:29:57.240 line:80%
I'm willing to give up everything.

00:29:57.250 --> 00:29:58.090 line:80%
Including...

00:30:12.900 --> 00:30:14.580 line:80%
I know it's hard for you, Lady.

00:30:15.180 --> 00:30:16.020 line:80%
But I have to

00:30:16.420 --> 00:30:18.140 line:80%
ask this of you.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:33.020 line:80%
The Bliss Palace is full of traps.

00:30:33.580 --> 00:30:34.860 line:80%
The troops of the Demonic Camp are

00:30:35.020 --> 00:30:36.420 line:80%
(Bliss Palace)
stationed at Yaoyue Pass.

00:30:36.520 --> 00:30:37.540 line:80%
At dusk, during You hour,

00:30:37.940 --> 00:30:38.980 line:80%
we'll set out at once.

00:30:39.140 --> 00:30:40.660 line:80%
Reach the Yaoyue Pass by You hour,

00:30:40.860 --> 00:30:43.260 line:80%
launch the attack at Xu hour.

00:30:43.260 --> 00:30:44.300 line:80%
Count us in for the attack on

00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:45.140 line:80%
Bliss Palace.

00:30:49.260 --> 00:30:50.100 line:80%
Zhao.

00:30:51.260 --> 00:30:52.500 line:80%
Let's step outside first.

00:30:52.500 --> 00:30:54.380 line:80%
Let Miss Cai and the Mr. Mu
talk in peace.

00:31:11.020 --> 00:31:11.860 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:12.460 --> 00:31:13.300 line:80%
A few months ago,

00:31:13.980 --> 00:31:15.180 line:80%
the masked man who snuck into

00:31:15.180 --> 00:31:16.940 line:80%
Qingque Sect and
kidnapped Chang Ning and me

00:31:16.940 --> 00:31:17.780 line:80%
was you.

00:31:17.780 --> 00:31:19.180 line:80%
You have sharp eyes, Miss.

00:31:19.180 --> 00:31:20.140 line:80%
It was indeed me.

00:31:27.020 --> 00:31:28.500 line:80%
You two were in cahoots all along!

00:31:31.180 --> 00:31:32.060 line:80%
Not the first time.

00:31:33.220 --> 00:31:34.500 line:80%
After the Chang Fort was destroyed,

00:31:34.900 --> 00:31:36.340 line:80%
I was ordered by Nie Zhe to

00:31:36.340 --> 00:31:37.900 line:80%
sneak into Qingque Sect
and catch Chang Ning.

00:31:38.340 --> 00:31:39.300 line:80%
I never thought

00:31:39.780 --> 00:31:41.460 line:80%
Chang Ning was
the long-lost Young Master.

00:31:42.420 --> 00:31:44.060 line:80%
And I even risked my life to save you.

00:31:45.140 --> 00:31:46.820 line:80%
Why aren't you acting in operas, Mr. Mu?

00:31:47.220 --> 00:31:48.060 line:80%
Such a pity.

00:31:49.820 --> 00:31:51.340 line:80%
Zhao loves watching plays so much,

00:31:51.580 --> 00:31:52.860 line:80%
if I don't put on a good act,

00:31:53.260 --> 00:31:54.740 line:80%
wouldn't that disappoint Zhao?

00:31:55.220 --> 00:31:57.620 line:80%
To preserve his strength
and eliminate Nie Zhe,

00:31:57.620 --> 00:31:59.420 line:80%
Mr. Mu endured humiliation
and bent when necessary.

00:31:59.420 --> 00:32:01.580 line:80%
Staying in a place
like Qingque Sect for months.

00:32:01.580 --> 00:32:02.980 line:80%
Truly, a model for us all.

00:32:03.580 --> 00:32:05.060 line:80%
A place like Qingque Sect?

00:32:05.320 --> 00:32:06.220 line:80%
Is it a terrible place?

00:32:06.460 --> 00:32:08.500 line:80%
Besides the ten years
I spent with my father,

00:32:08.900 --> 00:32:10.140 line:80%
the days at Qingque Sect

00:32:10.580 --> 00:32:11.540 line:80%
were the happiest

00:32:12.460 --> 00:32:13.620 line:80%
of my life.

00:32:16.620 --> 00:32:18.740 line:80%
You always mention your father.

00:32:18.740 --> 00:32:20.540 line:80%
Why never your mom?

00:32:22.220 --> 00:32:23.620 line:80%
- Mr. Mu' mother...
- Everyone,

00:32:23.620 --> 00:32:25.740 line:80%
Mr. Mu is still my child, after all.

00:32:25.740 --> 00:32:27.180 line:80%
I can't stop worrying about him.

00:32:27.780 --> 00:32:29.100 line:80%
Can you make an exception?

00:32:29.100 --> 00:32:30.500 line:80%
Let me see him once.

00:32:30.500 --> 00:32:32.100 line:80%
What the hell.

00:32:32.100 --> 00:32:33.620 line:80%
Speak of the devil, and she appears.

00:32:42.780 --> 00:32:43.620 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:32:45.780 --> 00:32:47.620 line:80%
Since hearing you're back,

00:32:48.500 --> 00:32:50.100 line:80%
my heart has been in turmoil.

00:32:50.100 --> 00:32:51.340 line:80%
I've thought of you day and night.

00:32:51.340 --> 00:32:53.100 line:80%
Only wish to see you once.

00:32:53.100 --> 00:32:54.500 line:80%
Seeing you so thin

00:32:55.140 --> 00:32:57.100 line:80%
truly breaks my heart.

00:32:57.100 --> 00:32:58.340 line:80%
I've been back for two months.

00:32:58.660 --> 00:33:00.020 line:80%
If you truly missed me,

00:33:00.620 --> 00:33:02.020 line:80%
why didn't you come sooner?

00:33:02.340 --> 00:33:04.220 line:80%
There are things beyond my control.

00:33:04.780 --> 00:33:05.980 line:80%
Nie Zhe…

00:33:05.980 --> 00:33:07.540 line:80%
He imprisoned me
within the Bliss Palace.

00:33:08.100 --> 00:33:09.140 line:80%
He called it protection.

00:33:09.140 --> 00:33:10.500 line:80%
But it was imprisonment and threats.

00:33:11.500 --> 00:33:13.220 line:80%
I miss you every day.

00:33:13.220 --> 00:33:14.620 line:80%
My heart wrenching in pain,

00:33:15.340 --> 00:33:17.140 line:80%
yet I could do nothing.

00:33:17.940 --> 00:33:20.660 line:80%
But I saw you going out to gather herbs.

00:33:22.980 --> 00:33:25.340 line:80%
You were the one at the Youming Path.

00:33:27.460 --> 00:33:29.140 line:80%
That was because
Nie Zhe forced me to go.

00:33:29.660 --> 00:33:30.580 line:80%
If I refuse to go,

00:33:31.220 --> 00:33:32.900 line:80%
he'd beat me brutally.

00:33:32.900 --> 00:33:34.220 line:80%
These days,

00:33:34.220 --> 00:33:35.820 line:80%
whenever he's upset,

00:33:35.820 --> 00:33:37.540 line:80%
he takes it out on me.

00:33:40.620 --> 00:33:42.740 line:80%
Though I live in hardship,

00:33:42.740 --> 00:33:45.660 line:80%
my longing and love for you

00:33:45.660 --> 00:33:47.500 line:80%
have never changed.

00:33:48.900 --> 00:33:50.100 line:80%
Qingyan, I just hope you

00:33:50.100 --> 00:33:52.340 line:80%
can understand your mother's hardships.

00:33:52.340 --> 00:33:54.300 line:80%
Your acting

00:33:54.300 --> 00:33:55.420 line:80%
still lacks some conviction.

00:33:56.340 --> 00:33:57.780 line:80%
If you truly want it to be convincing,

00:33:59.020 --> 00:34:01.420 line:80%
those wounds should look deeper.

00:34:01.980 --> 00:34:03.300 line:80%
More realistic that way.

00:34:03.740 --> 00:34:04.620 line:80%
Qingyan,

00:34:05.580 --> 00:34:07.180 line:80%
how can you speak to me like that?

00:34:08.580 --> 00:34:10.340 line:80%
I may have made mistakes in the past,

00:34:10.820 --> 00:34:12.140 line:80%
but my love for my son

00:34:12.140 --> 00:34:13.620 line:80%
is as clear as heaven and earth!

00:34:13.620 --> 00:34:15.430 line:80%
Spare me the "motherly love
and filial piety" nonsense!

00:34:19.780 --> 00:34:21.460 line:80%
We both know

00:34:21.820 --> 00:34:22.980 line:80%
what kind of people we are.

00:34:24.500 --> 00:34:25.660 line:80%
I tolerate you,

00:34:26.700 --> 00:34:27.900 line:80%
and I've let you stay this long.

00:34:28.300 --> 00:34:29.980 line:80%
Not because you gave birth to me,

00:34:30.900 --> 00:34:32.900 line:80%
but because I promised my father.

00:34:33.860 --> 00:34:35.980 line:80%
If you keep pushing your limits,

00:34:37.140 --> 00:34:38.420 line:80%
don't blame me

00:34:39.420 --> 00:34:40.780 line:80%
for being disrespectful.

00:34:45.220 --> 00:34:46.060 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:34:52.660 --> 00:34:53.500 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:34:53.740 --> 00:34:54.900 line:80%
This is your Fuying Sword.

00:34:54.900 --> 00:34:56.740 line:80%
You left it at
the Bliss Palace back then.

00:34:56.740 --> 00:34:58.060 line:80%
It belonged to your late father.

00:34:58.820 --> 00:35:00.060 line:80%
You must have missed it dearly.

00:35:00.620 --> 00:35:02.580 line:80%
I risked my life today to retrieve it.

00:35:03.580 --> 00:35:04.420 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:35:05.340 --> 00:35:06.820 line:80%
Will you trust me now?

00:35:13.060 --> 00:35:13.900 line:80%
Guanyue.

00:35:13.900 --> 00:35:14.740 line:80%
Yes.

00:35:14.740 --> 00:35:16.140 line:80%
Arrange a place for Madam to stay.

00:35:16.420 --> 00:35:17.260 line:80%
Madam.

00:35:17.620 --> 00:35:18.460 line:80%
Please come with me.

00:35:28.940 --> 00:35:29.980 line:80%
Your mother, she...

00:35:29.980 --> 00:35:30.940 line:80%
She's not my mother.

00:36:03.020 --> 00:36:03.860 line:80%
Dad.

00:36:12.460 --> 00:36:13.300 line:80%
The Dao's vessel

00:36:13.980 --> 00:36:15.460 line:80%
is never full.

00:36:16.700 --> 00:36:18.780 line:80%
This sword is named Fuying.
(*Fuying: Never full.)

00:36:19.460 --> 00:36:20.540 line:80%
May my son

00:36:22.420 --> 00:36:24.020 line:80%
live a long and peaceful life.

00:36:43.020 --> 00:36:43.900 line:80%
Father.

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:13.540 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

